text: Renuka Nagarkoti (रेनुका नगरकोटी) is a Nepali footballer who plays as a midfielder for APF Club and represents the Nepal women's national football team. ==Career== At club level, Bhandari plays for APF Club. ==International career== Renuka Nagarkoti represents Nepal at the international level. She is current the Nepali national team vice captain ==References== Category:Living people Category:Nepal women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Nepalese women's footballers
